<article data-history-node-id="941" role="article" about="/closureemergency-notice/oregon-schools-closed-19-20-school-year" class="node node--type-closure-emergency-notice node--view-mode-full"><h2>
      <a href="/closureemergency-notice/oregon-schools-closed-19-20-school-year" rel="bookmark"><span>Oregon Schools CLOSED for 19-20 School Year</span>
</a>
    </h2>
    

  
  <div class="node__content">
    
            <div>
<p>In response to continued efforts due to COVID-19, Oregon's Governor announced on April 8 that all schools will be closed for the rest of the 2019-20 school year. View the <a href="https://www.oregon.gov/newsroom/Pages/NewsDetail.aspx?newsid=36318" rel="nofollow"><strong>Governor's Press Release.</strong> </a>The Oregon Department of Education provided <strong><a href="https://www.oregon.gov/ode/students-and-family/healthsafety/Documents/Graduation%20Pathways%202020%20Guidance.pdf?utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=govdelivery" rel="nofollow">Graduation Pathways 2020 for Seniors</a></strong> and <strong><a href="https://www.oregon.gov/ode/students-and-family/healthsafety/Documents/Distance%20Learning%20for%20All%20Guidance%20March%202020.pdf?utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=govdelivery" rel="nofollow">Distance Learning for All Guidance. </a></strong></p>
<p>The Ione School District will provide updates on our website and Facebook page.</p>
</div>
      
