<article data-history-node-id="944" role="article" about="/article/notice-board-meeting" typeof="schema:Article" class="node node--type-article node--view-mode-full"><h2>
      <a href="/article/notice-board-meeting" rel="bookmark"><span property="schema:name">Notice of Board Meeting of Ione School District</span>
</a>
    </h2>
      <span property="schema:name" content="Notice of Board Meeting of Ione School District" class="hidden"></span>


  
  <div class="node__content">
    
            <div>  <img property="schema:image" src="/sites/ione.k12.or.us/files/styles/medium/public/images-attached/dreamstime_s_68379176.jpg?itok=ZcW3ymU2" width="220" height="165" alt="calendar page" typeof="foaf:Image">
</div>
      
            <div property="schema:text">
<p>NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN that the Ione School District Board of Directors will meet via the virtual platform ZOOM for a Work Session and regular Board Meeting on Tuesday, April 28, 2020. The Work Session will begin at 3:30 PM, with the regular Board Meeting to follow at 4:30 PM.</p>
<p><a class="file file--mime-application-pdf file--application-pdf" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="b5b27464-3801-4359-bf61-487401699283" href="/sites/ione.k12.or.us/files/inline-files/Ione%20SD_Work%20Session%20Agenda.pdf" rel="nofollow">Work Session Agenda</a><br><a class="file file--mime-application-pdf file--application-pdf" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="31083db3-45ac-4488-8e98-d7f12c5e2049" href="/sites/ione.k12.or.us/files/inline-files/Ione%20SD_Board%20Meeting%20Agenda.pdf" rel="nofollow">Board Meeting Agenda</a></p>
<p>
To make a Public Comment during the regular board meeting, please fill out the attached form and return to <span class="spamspan"><span class="u">kim.thul</span><img class="spamspan-image" alt="at" src="/modules/spamspan/image.gif"><span class="d">imesd.k12.or.us</span></span> or fax to 541-966-3240 by 5:00 pm on Monday, April 27. The form will be included in the board packets to discuss during the meeting. This meeting is open to the public to listen to via zoom. Just click on the link below and follow the instructions to connect.</p>
<p><a class="file file--mime-application-pdf file--application-pdf" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="530ff61f-6d30-4fb6-98a9-ccc826b80d93" href="/sites/ione.k12.or.us/files/inline-files/Ione%20SD_Public%20Comment%20Form.pdf" rel="nofollow">Public Comment Form</a></p>
<p>
Join Zoom Meeting<br><a href="https://zoom.us/j/98660558135">https://zoom.us/j/98660558135</a><br>
Meeting ID: 986 6055 8135</p>
<p>One tap mobile<br>
+16699006833,,98660558135# US (San Jose)<br>
+13462487799,,98660558135# US (Houston)</p>
<p>If you have any questions regarding the meeting, please contact Kim Thul at 541-966-3157 or by the email listed above.</p>
