            <div property="schema:text">
<p>Ione School District has prepared its Student Investment Account application and welcomes your input at the April 28, 2020 Board Meeting. The meeting will be held via Zoom. Please contact the District Office about connection information. You may also provide input in writing. The input may be sent via email to <span class="spamspan"><span class="u">jon.peterson</span><img class="spamspan-image" alt="at" src="/modules/spamspan/image.gif"><span class="d">ionesd.org</span><span class="e"><!--rel="nofollow"--></span></span> or postal delivery to P.O. Box 167, Ione, Oregon 97843.</p>
