<article data-history-node-id="940" role="article" about="/article/desk-and-locker-clean-out-april-20th" typeof="schema:Article" class="node node--type-article node--view-mode-full"><h2>
      <a href="/article/desk-and-locker-clean-out-april-20th" rel="bookmark"><span property="schema:name">Desk and Locker Clean Out April 20th</span>
</a>
    </h2>
      <span property="schema:name" content="Desk and Locker Clean Out April 20th" class="hidden"></span>


  
  <div class="node__content">
    
            <div>  <img property="schema:image" src="/sites/ione.k12.or.us/files/styles/medium/public/images-attached/dreamstime_s_162343583.jpg?itok=3svQI-id" width="220" height="147" alt="red lockers" typeof="foaf:Image">
</div>
      
            <div property="schema:text">
<p>Dear Parents and Students,</p>
<p>Ione Community School staff will be conducting desk and locker clean outs on Monday, April 20th. We ask that students come to the school on Tuesday, April 21<sup>st</sup> between the hours of 8 am – 12 pm. Since we have no way of knowing who has PE or athletic clothing in the locker rooms, we will have staff members available to escort students one at a time to their PE lockers to clean them out. We are still encouraging continued social distancing, so we ask that students and parents remain in their cars or continue to stay 6 feet away from each other. If you have any further questions, please contact us at 541 422-7131.</p>
<p>Estimados Padres y Estudiantes,</p>
<p>El personal de la Escuela Comunitaria de Ione llevará a cabo conducir la limpiada de escritorios y casilleros el lunes 20 de abril.   Pedimos que los estudiantes vengan a la escuela el martes 21 de abril entre las 8 am – 12 pm.  Dado que no tenemos forma de saber quién tiene ropa de educación fiscal o de atletismo en los vestuarios, tendremos miembros del personal disponibles para acompañar a los estudiantes de uno a uno a sus casilleros de PE para limpiarlos.  Seguimos fomentando el continuo distanciamiento social, pedimos que los estudiantes y los padres permanezcan en sus carros o continúan de permanecer 6 pies de distancia de otra gente. Si tiene mas preguntas, por favor contáctenos al 541-422-7131.</p>
</div>
      
  <div>
